<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AITAP70A4106021" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Controllo funzionale del servofreno
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Prima di effettuare questo controllo, verificare che non vi sia aria all&#39;interno del circuito idraulico.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "AITAP70A4106021001">
<title>
Controllo di tenuta
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Avviare il motore.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Arrestare il motore dopo averlo tenuto in moto per circa 1 o 2 minuti.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Premere ripetutamente il pedale del freno con la stessa forza usata per una normale frenata ed osservare come varia la corsa del pedale. Se la corsa del pedale diminuisce ad ogni pressione, il servofreno non perde aria.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.619mm" ver = "01" gw = "131" gh = "126"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.501in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.579in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.631in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
2ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
3ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Se la corsa del pedale non varia, il servofreno non tiene l&#39;aria.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
In caso di anomalia, controllare tubazioni e tenute del circuito della depressione e sostituire le parti difettose. Successivamente, ripetere l&#39;intera prova.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.196mm" ver = "01" gw = "132" gh = "125"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.030in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ª, 2ª, 3ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AITAP70A4106021002">
<title>
Controllo funzionale
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Con il motore spento, premere ripetutamente il pedale del freno sempre con la stessa forza e assicurarsi che la corsa del pedale resti immutata.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.323mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Avviare il motore premendo contemporaneamente il pedale del freno. Se la corsa del pedale aumenta di poco, il servofreno funziona a dovere. Nessuna variazione della corsa del pedale indica malfunzionamento del servofreno.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410008.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.958mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AITAP70A4106021003">
<title>
Controllo di tenuta sotto carico
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Con il motore in moto, premere il pedale del freno. Arrestare quindi il motore mantenendo premuto il pedale del freno.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.805mm" ver = "01" gw = "123" gh = "130"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.232in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.628in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Pressione
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Mantenere premuto il pedale del freno per 30 secondi. Se l&#39;altezza del pedale resta immutata, il servofreno funziona. Se l&#39;altezza del pedale varia, il servofreno non funziona a dovere.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.059mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "131"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.643in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.800in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Pressione
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
T:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
30 secondi
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
